<h2>What's Next?</h2>
<p>
    I have always been interested in data journalism and in finding ways for statistics to tell a story or illuminate a
    set of truths. We all have perceptions of what we think it true, and it is fun to use statistics and charts to
    confirm or deny one's perceptions.</p>
<p>
    My next steps will be to see if newer restrictions cause traffic level to start decreasing again. I plan to
    analyze holiday travel and compare it to previous years where possible. I will also look at hourly traffic data, and
    see if rush hour traffic changes are more or less dramatic than overall daily counts. Lastly, I plan to aggregate
    all the various counters into one figure, rather than analyze locations individually.
</p>